      "writtenOn": "2019-01-22T19:24:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "switch {\n  case err \u003d\u003d ds.ErrNoSuchEntity:\n    return ErrNotFound\n  case err !\u003d nil:\n    return transient.Tag.Apply(err)\n}\n\n(and below too)\n\nMarking errors as transient is extremely useful when implementing good retry strategies.",
